<tr id="L63"><td><a href="#L63">63</a></td><td>SPOCK:  Sir, we have completely scanned your planet. We find it highly advanced, prosperous in a material sense, comfortable for your people, and peaceful in the extreme. Yet you say you are at war. There is no evidence of this.</td></tr>

<tr id="L64"><td><a href="#L64">64</a></td><td>ANAN:  Casualties among our civilian population total from one to three million dead each year from direct enemy attack. That is one reason, Captain, why we told you to stay away. As long as your ship is orbiting our planet, it is in severe danger.</td></tr>

