<tr id="L113"><td><a href="#L113">113</a></td><td>ANAN:  Oh, no, quite real. An attack is mathematically launched. I lost my wife in the last attack. Our civilisation lives. The people die, but our culture goes on.</td></tr>

<tr id="L114"><td><a href="#L114">114</a></td><td>KIRK:  You mean to tell me your people just walk into a disintegration machine when they're told to?</td></tr>

